<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">You need to contact the person who hosted the giveaway - they won&apos;t see your message on here. Have a look at the email that told you you won and it wi<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">You need to contact the person who hosted the giveaway - they won't see your message on here. Have a look at the email that told you you won and it will tell you who to contact. :)<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
