  <span id="freeText10730040504823753958" style="display:none">This book seems to be everywhere. I think the back cover is selling it. After her aunt dies, a woman decides to see if she can find her other aunt. Then we learn the aunt's story about life on Sardinia in the 1950s. I kept reading to find out what happened, but I never really cared about the characters or the story itself. </span>
