<span id="freeTextContainer3181773245811022275">I won this book through the Goodreads website giveaway. I found the story very very romantic and got carried away with Carmela and her lover !!! I found the descriptions of the countryside and the scenes very explicit and sometimes carried on a bit too much and would rather have had more of the story, I must admit that the ending left me breathless and quite surprised. I did not expect it in one way but in another way I kind of knew it would end up like that. A brilliant novel that I loved to re</span>
  <span id="freeText3181773245811022275" style="display:none">I won this book through the Goodreads website giveaway. I found the story very very romantic and got carried away with Carmela and her lover !!! I found the descriptions of the countryside and the scenes very explicit and sometimes carried on a bit too much and would rather have had more of the story, I must admit that the ending left me breathless and quite surprised. I did not expect it in one way but in another way I kind of knew it would end up like that. A brilliant novel that I loved to read and I was so happy to find out that Carmela did follow her heart after all! Happy for that wonderful ending !!!</span>
