        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2027662582" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer5549721026277631628">At first, I found this book a little bit difficult to get into. I found that the story was a bit slow, with nothing happening between Joe and Carmela. However, about more than halfway through the book, it took an unexpected turn, and it got much better. I really enjoyed the love that was expressed between Joe and Carmela, although I did feel as though their love scenes were a bit rushed, with them being explained in little detail. I also loved how the story ended, although I kind of had a feelin</span>
  <span id="freeText5549721026277631628" style="display:none">At first, I found this book a little bit difficult to get into. I found that the story was a bit slow, with nothing happening between Joe and Carmela. However, about more than halfway through the book, it took an unexpected turn, and it got much better. I really enjoyed the love that was expressed between Joe and Carmela, although I did feel as though their love scenes were a bit rushed, with them being explained in little detail. I also loved how the story ended, although I kind of had a feeling that was how it would end. Overall, a pretty good book once it was at the end however, it started out a bit sluggish.</span>
  <a data-text-id="5549721026277631628" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

