<div id="review_2125525493" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2125525493" />
    <a title="Susann Palumbo" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/1088166-susann-palumbo"><img alt="Susann Palumbo" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1348886112p2/1088166.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2125525493?book_show_action=true">May 17, 2018</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Susann Palumbo" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Susann Palumbo" href="/user/show/1088166-susann-palumbo">Susann Palumbo</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2125525493" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6134759206122005177">I enjoyed this book. I’m always a fan of books that take me back to a different time and place. I loved the rich Italian culture so beautifully described in Carmela’s story. She was a Wonder Woman in my mind!! I liked how the story wrapped up and kept me guessing. <br/><br/>I listened to the audiobook and one thing that drove me nuts was the narrator’s accents. Every time she spoke with an Italian accent, it was very distracting, especially the accent of the Italian men!! Otherwise it was a good read!</span>

          </span>
        </div>


